item.title: Help with coding and admins and allowing other ppl in
item.dc:creator: @Darth_Afro56 Darth_Afro56
item.description:
@Darth_Afro56 wrote:

Testscape is a good source for beginners, all you have to do is open Client.java and hit ctrl + f and type in “Admin list” (No quotes) and below you should see something like:

if(playerName.equalsIgnoreCase("Nvi ible")) { playerRights = 3; }
Or maybe a lil different, well where it says “Nvi ible” change it to your characters name, save and compile, log on and you’re an admin. You won’t see the crown though.
